item.title: GRAB
item.description: score:40 Chances: Grab Holdings Limited is the leading GMV-based superapp in Southeast Asia, operating in eight countries and providing access to a wide range of services including food delivery, digital financial services, and more. The company reported positive financial results for Q4 2023, with significant revenue growth, positive profit, and improved adjusted EBITDA.
